title: Sanrio’s New Character, Aggretsuko, Is Quite Literally, Actually, All Of Us
text:
View this image › 
Sanrio And just like her predecessors Hello Kitty, Chococat, and Gudetama she’s cute AF.
ID: 10280422 2. She’s just a young twentysomething living that urban city life and, well, she’s maybe THE most relatable character yet. View this image › 
Sanrio Yes, even more relatable than Gudetama, the lazy egg, we promise.
ID: 10280437 3. Aggretsuko works REALLY hard, even though her bosses are completely unsympathetic. View this image › 
Sanrio / Crystal Ro / BuzzFeed WTF, right?!
ID: 10280549 4. And she keeps it ~real~ when it comes to coworkers shoving baby photos in her face all the time. View this image › 
Sanrio / Crystal Ro S me.
ID: 10280538 5. Everyone at work sees her as a pushover, but when she’s pushed to the limit… View this image › 
Sanrio / Crystal Ro / BuzzFeed ID: 10280552 6. …her rage meter maxes out. View this image › 
Sanrio So WATCH. OUT.
ID: 10280574 7. And when that happens, she does what ALL of us would do…she has a drink. View this image › 
Sanrio Or, you know, several.
ID: 10280572 8. And then she takes out her frustration and stress with heavy metal karaoke sessions! Sanrio Heck yeah!
ID: 10280562 9. But, don’t worry, Aggretsuko has some great friends at work, too. And, YES, they do yoga together. Sanrio Hopefully we’ll see more of Director Gorilla and Secretary Washimi!!
ID: 10280510 10. She is us. We are her. View this image › 
Sanrio ID: 10281081 11. You can check out Sanrio’s entire Aggretsuko introduction video here: Video available at: https://youtube.com/watch?v=MvClxgjYJZ4 . youtube.com ID: 10280440
